  <owl:Ontology rdf:about="http://ontology.amt.org/amt-ontology-full">
    <dcterms:title>AMT Ontology -- reasoner-ready bundle (schema + externals + fixtures, self-contained)</dcterms:title>
    <owl:versionInfo>1.0.0</owl:versionInfo>
    <rdfs:comment>Self-contained merge of the AMT schema, internal + external CodeSets, pseudonymized fixture individuals, gUFO, and the OMG Commons modules referenced by the schema. All owl:imports have been stripped: a reasoner can load this single file with no network access. Built by publish/build_reasoner_ready.py from 31 source files. See README.md for reasoner-choice notes.</rdfs:comment>
  </owl:Ontology>
