      </amtmeta:Collection>
    </skos:closeMatch>
    <rdfs:comment>closeMatch via umbrella: pc_ecs:bucketJoiningAndForming groups bucketForming + bucketWelding via amtmeta:groups, covering both forming and welding-style fabrication. Same-grain mapping at the umbrella level.</rdfs:comment>
