  <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#isAspectProperPartOf">
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">isAspectProperPartOf</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Identifies a gufo:Aspect of which the aspect is a proper part.

For example, John's obligations towards Mary in the scope of their marriage is an aspect proper part of their marriage  (and same can be said of Mary's extrinsic aspects in the scope of their marriage.)

This property can be used to represent the composition of a relator from extrisinc aspects, but also to represent complex extrisinc aspects.

gufo:isAspectProperPartOf is transitive.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Aspect"/>
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#isProperPartOf"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty"/>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Aspect"/>
  </owl:ObjectProperty>
