    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://ontology.amt.org/im#Company"/>
    <rdfs:comment>Links a record to its corporate entity. Domain im:Registration (v0.6.1) covers VisitorRecord, ExhibitorRecord, AmtFacility, and external exhibitor sub-Kinds (e.g. pc_jimtof_cs:Exhibitor). Target Company IRI is hash-derived from the normalized company name so identical companies across record types collapse to one entity.</rdfs:comment>
