      <owl:Restriction rdf:nodeID="n234f9bcb19864ff6b7dc566604c500d7b55">
        <owl:maxCardinality rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#nonNegativeInteger">1</owl:maxCardinality>
        <owl:onProperty rdf:resource="http://ontology.amt.org/im#hasMTRole"/>
      </owl:Restriction>
    </rdfs:subClassOf>
    <rdfs:comment>Long-running AMT membership relationship. Sibling of im:Registration under gufo:Relator (not a sub-Kind -- Registration is per-show, Membership is org-level). Mediates one im:Member (the company) and one im:Association (im:AMT in practice). One Membership instance per Company; renewals extend the same instance rather than minting a new one. Carries the org-level membership-application attributes: im:hasMTRole (bylaw-defined member type) and im:hasPrimaryProductLine (coarse business segment). Lifecycle fields like memberSinceDate / dues / memberClass are not modeled here yet -- they will land when AMT supplies a Salesforce export carrying those columns (see docs/decisions/im.md).</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:label>Membership</rdfs:label>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class"/>
  </gufo:Kind>
