  <owl:ObjectProperty rdf:about="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#isSubQuantityOf">
    <rdfs:subPropertyOf rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#isObjectProperPartOf"/>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">isSubQuantityOf</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:domain rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Quantity"/>
    <rdf:type rdf:resource="http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#TransitiveProperty"/>
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Identifies a gufo:Quantity of which the quantity is a part.

For example, the quantity of water in a wine glass is a sub-quantity of the wine in that glass.

gufo:isSubQuantityOf is transitive (Guizzardi, 2005, p. 184).

Sub-quantities are always essential parts of their wholes. Thus, gufo:standsInQualifiedParthood is not applicable for sub-quantities.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:range rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Quantity"/>
  </owl:ObjectProperty>
