  <owl:Class rdf:about="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#FunctionalComplex">
    <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">A complex gufo:Object whose parts (components) play different roles in its composition. 

For example, a person could be considered a gufo:FunctionalComplex with the various organs (heart, brain, lungs, etc.) playing different roles. Another example is a scrum team, which is composed by people playing the roles of scrum master, product owner, developer, etc.

To explicitly capture temporary components, use gufo:TemporaryParthoodSituation.</rdfs:comment>
    <rdfs:comment rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#isComponentOf"/>
    <rdfs:label xml:lang="en">FunctionalComplex</rdfs:label>
    <rdfs:subClassOf rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#Object"/>
    <rdfs:seeAlso rdf:resource="http://purl.org/nemo/gufo#TemporaryParthoodSituation"/>
  </owl:Class>
